Text: FW PemexEnronKMI LOI Original Message From Matney David Sent Wednesday July AM To Matney David Subject RE PemexEnronKMI LOI Kim Sorry I have not replied to your phone call I am out of town and been tied up in meetings Our attorney who reviewed the LOI is still on vacation and will not return until next week As soon as he returns I will have him look at the LOI supplied to us by Pemex and make our revisions I will be out next week on vacation and will not return until the first part of August In my absence I will see if Bruce Page can pursue getting the LOI to you Original Message From Matney David Sent Tuesday July PM To Kimberly nroncom Subject PemexEnronKMI LOI Per my telephone call File TransPecosPEMEXloicomparetTdoc
